&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your mission &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an innovative aerospace company entering production, we are seeking a highly motivated, hands-on Production Supervisor to lead and shape the foundation of our manufacturing operations. You’ll be the first in this critical role, with the opportunity to influence everything from layout design to process systems, ensuring a world-class operation from day one.&lt;/p&gt;
