&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design and layout of the new production floor, including work cells, flow, and equipment placement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate, recommend, and coordinate procurement of production machinery and tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement tool control systems, safety protocols, and standard operating procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the selection and setup of an MRP/ERP system, with a focus on production tracking, inventory control, and quality integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Leadership &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hire, train, and supervise a team of skilled technicians and operators.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish a high-performance culture of accountability, continuous improvement, and safety.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide hands-on guidance and mentorship on technical and procedural matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively develop training programs to address team and company needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Production Management &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage day-to-day production activities, ensuring schedule adherence, quality standards, and efficiency targets are met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineering on manufacturability feedback and process optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and monitor KPIs and drive root cause analysis for production issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement best practices and streamlined processes to ensure products are completed safely, with the highest quality, and delivered on time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You&#39;ll Bring These Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in a production or manufacturing leadership role, ideally in aerospace or high-precision industries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience setting up or scaling a manufacturing facility.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of lean manufacturing, tool control systems, and production flow optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
