&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;4630&quot; data-local-id=&quot;7252f87ae9a5&quot;&gt;As a Senior/Staff Software Engineer on the Flight Software Team, you are responsible for all aspects the development of the software on the aircraft. You will interface with other engineers to develop and understand requirements, architect and writing high quality code, build tests and test infrastructure, documentation, and provide support through the software lifecycle. You will report to the Manager of Flight Software and collaborate with other engineers as part of a multi-functional team.&lt;/p&gt;
