&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;5520&quot; data-local-id=&quot;f0c3038474c4&quot;&gt;Create highly reliable embedded software that control critical systems on Heart’s aircraft.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;5615&quot; data-local-id=&quot;4a21fcf9cf5f&quot;&gt;Work with interdisciplinary teams to scope, design and build next generation hybrid electric aircraft capabilities, including engine controllers, battery management systems, flight control actuators, flight control systems and aircraft data networks.&lt;/p&gt;
