&lt;li&gt;Write reliable, maintainable code for embedded environments including microcontrollers, bare-metal systems, RTOS, and embedded operating systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with systems, hardware, flight sciences, and quality teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to verification and validation activities including unit testing, integration testing, and system-level testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support simulation, modeling, and test activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document designs, requirements, and test results clearly and effectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
