&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your mission&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated Turbomachinery Engineer to join our Propulsion team. You will lead the design and integration of the turbomachinery components, including the fuel system and pitch control system. You will interface across mechanical, thermal, electrical, and control systems to deliver a fully integrated and certifiable propulsion unit.&lt;/p&gt;
