&lt;li&gt;This role is a Responsible Engineer (RE) focuses on the integration of turbomachinery into our hybrid aircraft.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full ownership over design, fabrication, and certification of the hybrid powertrain.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design of turbomachinery, including combustion systems, fluid analysis, exhaust, high-speed rotating machinery, and similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and execute system-level tests, such as engine and propeller test stands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with suppliers to ensure delivery of integrated, certifiable subsystems.&lt;/li&gt;
